@KASM_Capital Theres no cure

I held a lot of AMD like 70% of my port at $210 then I sold semi and jumped on photonics and $SIVE

$SIVE is up 300% and overall my accounts are about 100% YTD but  I still feel like I missed out on AMD when its only up about 35% from when I had it

@SixSigmaCapital People are catching on CPU Bottleneck $ARM $AMD $NVDA Just like memory and photonics! 
For AI Super cycle! Insane though 

$ARM pivot to CPUs was big one , went too fast

